text: David Ogilvy (7 June 1859 - 6 August 1917) was an Australian cricketer. He played two first-class matches for New South Wales between 1885/86 and 1886/87. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1859 births Category:1917 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney
